ABOUT THE WHOLE THING.

39:43.859 --> 39:45.774
I'M GONNA MAKE A TON
OF MONEY ON THIS DEAL.

39:46.601 --> 39:48.342
SO WHAT DO YOU SAY, YOU
WANT TO BE MY PARTNER?

39:50.083 --> 39:50.953
-I GOTTA GO.

39:51.606 --> 39:52.738
-AREN'T YOU GONNA
FINISH YOUR BEER?

39:52.868 --> 39:53.826
-NO, I'M DONE.

39:57.743 --> 39:58.961
AND SO ARE YOU.

40:09.276 --> 40:10.451
-SID: HI, MITCH.
-HEY, SID.

40:19.504 --> 40:20.853
-C.J.: WELL HAVE FUN SURFING.

40:20.983 --> 40:22.463
I'LL SEE YOU LATER FOR DINNER.

40:22.594 --> 40:24.944
-C.J., THANKS FOR EVERYTHING.

40:33.953 --> 40:34.693
HEY, MITCH.

40:34.823 --> 40:35.781
-HEY.

40:35.911 --> 40:37.347
-WHAT HAPPENS TO NEELY?

40:37.478 --> 40:40.307
-SHE WAS FIRED. YOU
WANT TO PRESS CHARGES?

40:41.047 --> 40:43.136
-NO THANKS, I JUST WANT
TO GO ON WITH MY LIFE.

40:43.266 --> 40:44.224
-GOOD MAN.

40:46.748 --> 40:49.621
HA! [LAUGHING]

40:49.751 --> 40:51.753
-THESE ARE JAMS, THEY'RE
THE COOLEST THINGS OUT.

40:51.884 --> 40:53.494
-THOSE ARE OLD NEWS.

40:53.625 --> 40:55.540
I WAS WEARING THOSE WHEN
YOU WERE WEARING DIAPERS.

40:56.192 --> 40:58.412
-WELL THAT SHOWS YOU, WHAT
GOES AROUND COMES AROUND.

41:00.458 --> 41:01.415
BEST CAR?

41:01.546 --> 41:03.548
-427 CHEVY COBRA.

41:04.287 --> 41:06.333
-NO WAY, FERRARI TESTAROSSA,
NOW THAT'S A CAR.

41:06.464 --> 41:07.856
-YOU'VE GOTTA BE KIDDING.

41:07.987 --> 41:09.510
I MEAN, IF YOU LIKE
REFINED AND BORING.

41:09.641 --> 41:12.513
ME, I LIKE AN ENGINE THAT
TURNS TO A TRANSMISSION

41:12.644 --> 41:14.515
WITH TWO SEATS
ALONG FOR THE RIDE.

41:15.255 --> 41:16.256
GOOD TO HAVE YOU BACK, PAL.

41:16.386 --> 41:17.170
-GLAD TO BE BACK.

41:17.300 --> 41:18.345
BEST LEAD GUITAR?

41:18.476 --> 41:20.739
-CARLOS SANTANA
WITHOUT A DOUBT.

41:20.869 --> 41:24.917
-JUST ONE DOUBT, SLASH,
GUNS 'N ROSES ALL THE WAY.

41:25.047 --> 41:26.527
-BEST LEAD SINGER?

41:26.658 --> 41:28.442
-MATT: ARE YOU KIDDING?
DAVID HASSELHOFF.

41:28.573 --> 41:30.052
-MITCH: WELL,
HE'S BIG IN EUROPE.

41:30.183 --> 41:32.577
-MATT: ANYWAYS,
STAY OFF MY WAVE, OKAY?

41:32.707 --> 41:33.839
-MITCH: STAY OFF MY WAVE.

41:33.969 --> 41:35.362
JUST TRY TO STAY UP WITH ME.

41:36.668 --> 41:38.974
-[ENDING THEME]
